Interface IAttributes

All Known Subinterfaces:
IEntity, INPC, IPlayer
All Known Implementing Classes:
DerivedAttributes, Entity, Levels, MainAttributes, Proficiencies
public interface IAttributes
Defines the structure for character attributes, including base attributes, derived attributes, overdrive attributes, weapon proficiencies, armor proficiencies, skill proficiencies, life proficiencies, and personal proficiencies.
